N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 ยง 209.4 - Emissions other than total fluorides

State Regulations

Emissions of air contaminants other than total fluorides
from any air contamination source in a primary aluminum reduction plant are
regulated by all other applicable Parts of this Subchapter. Notes
